description: In a bedroom, a couple is in bed. The wife is sitting upright, while the husband who is speaking is laying down. Next to the bed is a nightstand under a window. Through the window is a view of outer space, with all of Earth visible. The window is open with the curtains drawn.
caption: It's just the wind.
element: This is a play on words on the dual meaning of wind to mean either typical wind or solar wind.

description: In a social setting, several people are standing in a room wearing business attire and holding drinks. Two couples face each other, but the man in one of the couples is dressed in a full, vintage-style deep-sea diving suit, complete with a helmet and a hose attached to the back, looking somewhat uncomfortable.
caption: We don't have much of a sex life, but he's good at finding keys in the swimming pool.
element: The woman implies that the man never takes off the suit, even at home

description: On a frozen lake, a man sits on a bucket next to an ice-fishing hut, holding a fishing rod. Instead of a traditional round hole, the ice has been cut into a person-shaped silhouette, with the fishing line lowered into the outline. Nearby, another man stands watching the scene, bundled up in winter clothing.
caption: He's got a new fish-whispering technique.
element: A third person is implied to be under the ice, suggested by the human-shaped hole.

description: In a grand church, there is a large bar stocked with bottles of liquor. A few patrons are seated at the bar, and sunbeams stream through the stained glass windows, dramatically illuminating one of the patrons. A couple dressed in formal church attire stands at the open doors, with the husband speaking.
caption: Finally—a faith-based initiative I can embrace.
element: The government funding the church to run a bar would be illegal and absurd

description: In an unusually large and sparsely furnished room, a circular, solid barrier decorated with stars encloses a small seating area. Inside the enclosure, two individuals, appearing very small in comparison to the vast room, sit in armchairs, each holding a glass of wine, seemingly engaged in a casual conversation. The enclosed space includes side tables with lamps, emphasizing a cozy yet isolated atmosphere within the expansive and minimally decorated surroundings.
caption: The people who lived here before had lions.
element: Lions are indeed cats, and suit the circus setting

description: In a stone-walled balcony scene, a robed king wearing a crown stands within an arched recess. In front of him, two attendants in medieval-style clothing each hold large baskets and scatter paper currency down to a crowd with outstretched arms. Two other men, also in medieval clothing, stand off to the side on the balcony, speaking to each other.
caption: Looks like another ye olde stimulus package.
element: The caption is sarcastically criticizing stimulus packages

description: Two golfers stand on a grassy field, each holding golf clubs in bags slung over their shoulders. However, instead of a golf course, they are looking at a field filled with barbed wire, tanks, and machine guns. A golf flag is visible in the background, alongside scattered trees and clouds.
caption: I support our troops as much as the next guy, but do we have to let them play through?
element: Doing favors for military members is a common practice, but can sometimes be taken advantage of

description: A pregnant woman, wearing primitive clothing, sits on a large tree branch or vine, holding her belly and speaking. Tarzan, shirtless and wearing a loincloth, stands nearby, leaning against a tree. The background features trees and jungle foliage.
caption: Fine. If it's a boy, we'll call him Boy. But if it's a girl I want to call her McKenzie.
element: Couples deciding who gets to choose the name based on the gender is a common situation

description: On the ledge of a tall building in an urban cityscape, a man in a suit standing inside a window speaks to three individuals precariously standing on the ledge: a clergyman, a police officer, and a firefighter, all dressed in their respective uniforms, and positioned like they might jump off.
caption: Excuse me—does this joke need a lawyer?
element: This implies that the man in the suit (likely a lawyer) might also be suicidal, commenting on the profession

description: A person wearing a helmet and a harness labeled “PARACHUTE” falls off the edge of a cliff, flailing their arms. Another person stands on the cliff behind him, pushing them off the edge, speaking with a smile. The person pushing is wearing a tie.
caption: Great coaching is about helping others move forward.....
element: This would be extremely dangerous for the first time without instruction

description: Inside a workshop-like room, three elves in pointy hats sit at a long table with open laptop computers. The middle elf appears distressed and is speaking, while the two elves on either side look toward him.
caption: It’s from Santa, and it goes way, way beyond jolly.
element: This frames Santa as a boss making an inappropriate advance on an employee

description: A title reading “Inside the FDA” hangs above a lab-like room. Two people in lab coats stand in the corner reviewing notes on a clipboard. At a central table, a man in a lab coat sits facing forward, with piles of pills and some vials and a syringe in front of him, speaking. Another man, also in a lab coat, stands beside him, holding a clipboard.
caption: These medicines all taste pretty good—let’s approve them.
element: Taste-testing each medicine would be dangerous for the tester

description: Inside a workshop-like room, three elves in pointy hats sit at a long table with open laptop computers. The middle elf appears distressed and is speaking, while the two elves on either side look toward him.
caption: It’s from Santa, and it goes way, way beyond jolly.
element: "Beyond Jolly" is a Santa-specific way of describing romantic advances

description: In a restaurant, a man and a woman are sitting down to eat dressed in nice clothing. The man is leaning over the table with his hand on a glass looking at the woman with a soft smile. However, the man is bald, and has a cartoonishly large forehead, with the outline of the woman visible on his forehead. The woman, siting upright, is speaking.
caption: Well, it's a lovely gesture, but I still think we should start seeing other people.
element: This implies that the image on his forehead is a tattoo, as getting a tattoo of your significant other is a common practice

description: The cartoon shows a woman in her underwear sitting up in bed, looking forward with a disgruntled expression. A large snow globe with a snowman inside is positioned next to her on the bed. The woman is speaking.
caption: I think the Manhattan skyline is getting suspicious
element: This implies that she is cheating on her partner, a snowglobe of the manhattan skyline, with the snowman

A few patrons are seated at the bar, and sunbeams stream through the stained glass windows, dramatically illuminating one of the patrons. A couple dressed in formal church attire stands at the open doors, with the husband speaking.
caption: Finally—a faith-based initiative I can embrace.
element: This refers to President George W. Bush's "Faith-Based and Community Initiatives," a program that funds cetrain faith-based organizations

description: In an office setting, two people are sitting calmly at a desk, seemingly engaged in a business conversation. Meanwhile, through the large glass window behind them, a chaotic chase is unfolding as individuals dressed in business attire armed with various weapons— a hammer, bat, and gun—are running after another man, with his tie trailing him. One man sitting down is speaking to the other.
caption: How soon can you start?
element: This directly implies that the employee being chased in the background is leaving a vacancy at the company.

description: A doctor wearing a head mirror and standing behind a desk is in a typical doctor's offide. However, a giant hand is reaching through the doorway, facing up. The doctor is reaching over the desk to check the enormous hand's pulse.
caption: I don't know why you're so jolly—your cholesterol is through the roof.
element: This is a play on words. While "through the roof" typically means very elevated levels, here the giant patient is literally breaking through the roof.

description: In a bar setting, two individuals sit next to each other at the counter. One is a man in a suit and tie, holding a martini glass and speaking to the person beside him. The other person is wearing a full hazmat suit, complete with a helmet and radioactive symbol, and is holding a glass of liquid on a coaster. The bar features standard items like napkins, bottles, and a coffee pot, while a window behind them provides a view of the outside world.
caption: Trust me, background radiation—it's the new secondhand smoke.
element: This suggests that the man always wears the hazmat suit in his day-to-day life
